snippet.title: CHORUS - Accolades Trailer [4K]
snippet.description:
Many of you have joined the Resistance already and some have even learned the truth behind the meaning of Chorus. We are delighted to see so much positivity around Chorus and such a high praise from the reviews.

These are some of the highlights:
“A delightful surprise” – VG247

“A potent package” – Rock Paper Shotgun

“Flipping Marvellous” – The Xbox Hub

“Varied and Beautiful” – The Escapist

“Fantastic” - Screenrant
